<section class="ba-features ba-p50 primary-bg-light quality-block trf-quality-block">
<div class="container">
<div class="ba-features-wrap">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12 text-mg-center">
<h2 class="ba-h3 big">Compassionate Care, Tailored for You</h2>
<p class="f-sec-desc">At True Homecare, we believe in offering personalized care that respects your unique needs. Our compassionate team works closely with you to develop a care plan that supports your independence and enhances your wellbeing. We take the time to understand your requirements, ensuring you feel comfortable and supported every step of the way.
</p></div>
</div>
<div class="ba-features-list">
<div class="row ba-s-loop-gap text-mob-center">
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<img data-src="/wp-content/themes/understrap-child//img/top_customer_service_icon.svg" class="quality-block--icon ba-quality-icon lazyload" alt="" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" />
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<h3>Committed to Comfort and Quality</h3>
<p>Your comfort is our priority. From the moment you reach out, our dedicated team ensures that your care plan is not only effective but also reflects the high standards of quality you deserve. We deliver care that aligns with your lifestyle, allowing you to thrive at home.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4 ba-gutter-lg">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<img data-src="/wp-content/themes/understrap-child//img/topqualitymaterials.svg" class="quality-block--icon ba-quality-icon lazyload" alt="" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" />
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<h3>Where Expertise Meets Compassion</h3>
<p>Each member of our team brings a wealth of experience, training, and a genuine passion for providing exceptional care. We’re here to help you live comfortably and independently, with the support you need, when you need it.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<img data-src="/wp-content/themes/understrap-child//img/TopInstallationTeam.svg" class="quality-block--icon ba-quality-icon lazyload" alt="" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" />
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<h3>Care as Unique as You Are</h3>
<p>Every person is different, and so are their care needs. That’s why we offer flexible, bespoke care solutions that cater to your specific requirements. Whether it's companionship, specialist care, or assistance with daily tasks, we tailor our services to support your health, happiness, and wellbeing at home.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="ba-2block-bg ba-gap-lg block-col-and-video">
<div class="container">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="block-with-bg">
<div class="ba-left-bg-full lazyload" style="background:inherit;" data-bg="url(&#039;/wp-content/themes/understrap-child/img/quality_bg.jpg&#039;)"></div>
<h5>Personalised Care, Tailored for You</h5>
<h2>Personalised Care, Tailored for You</h2>
<p>At True Homecare, we’re dedicated to helping you stay in the comfort of your own home. Our services are fully customized to meet the unique needs of each client, ensuring the best possible care.
We carefully match each client with a certified, experienced care provider who offers flexible and professional support, designed to enhance your independence and wellbeing.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6 ba-m-hide">
<div class="ba-left-bg-full" id="video-container">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
