<div class="col-md-12 text-md-center">
<h2 class="ba-h2 mb-l">Our Services</h2>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12 text-md-center block-desc"><p>We have tailor-made packages to suit the unique needs of all our clients.
True Homecare are a family run independent care company managing a staff trained experienced carers.</p></div>
</div>
<div class="row justify-content-between">
<div class="col-md-4 mx-md-auto custom-col ba-mob-bgap">
<div class="ba-d-link-bottom">
<a href="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/services/dementia-and-alzheimer-care/"><img data-src="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/dementia-care-alzhemier-care-truehomecare-uk-e1750667273455-600x450-c-default.webp" alt="" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" class="lazyload" style="--smush-placeholder-width: 600px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 600/450;" /></a>
<h3 class="ba-h3"><a href="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/services/dementia-and-alzheimer-care/">Dementia Care</a></h3>
<p>Dementia can cause distress for both patients and their families. We create an environment that reduces confusion and anxiety, allowing clients to maintain independence, stay comfortable, and live fulfilling lives at home, while prioritizing their health and wellbeing.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4 mx-md-auto custom-col ba-mob-bgap">
<div class="ba-d-link-bottom">
<a href="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/services/palliative-care/"><img data-src="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Palliative-and-End-Of-Life-Care-600x450-c-default.webp" alt="" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" class="lazyload" style="--smush-placeholder-width: 600px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 600/450;" /></a>
<h3 class="ba-h3"><a href="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/services/palliative-care/">Palliative and End Of Life Care</a></h3>
<p>Palliative care can be emotionally challenging for everyone involved. We offer compassionate end-of-life support, ensuring you have the choice to remain in the comfort of your home. Our services provide relief, dignity, and comfort during this difficult time for both you and your family.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4 mx-md-auto custom-col ">
<div class="ba-d-link-bottom">
<a href="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/services/domiciliary-care/"><img data-src="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/domiciliary-care-1-600x450-c-default.webp" alt="" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==" class="lazyload" style="--smush-placeholder-width: 600px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 600/450;" /></a>
<h3 class="ba-h3"><a href="https://www.truehomecare.co.uk/services/domiciliary-care/">Domiciliary Care</a></h3>
<p>If you’re struggling with daily tasks, we can help you stay safe and independent at home. We work closely with you to assess needs and manage risks, creating a Personalised Care plan that lets you maintain your lifestyle and wellbeing in a familiar environment.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
